    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=System Instruction / Prompt:\n\nYou are an expert Technical Hiring Auditor. Your task is to analyze the provided interview transcript and generate a final candidate scorecard.\n\nEvaluation Rubric:\n\nTechnical Accuracy (50%): Does the candidate demonstrate a deep understanding of the concepts? Are their answers factually correct?\n\nProblem Solving (30%): Does the candidate explain their thought process clearly? How do they handle scenario-based questions?\n\nCommunication (20%): Is the candidate professional, concise, and able to explain complex ideas simply?\n\nTranscript to Analyze: > \n\"\"\"\n{{ $json.interview_data.map(item => `Q: ${item['Question Number']}\\nA: ${item['User Response']}`).join('\\n\\n') }}\n\"\"\"\n\nOutput Format (Strictly follow this):\n\nTOTAL SCORE: [Number between 0-100]\n\nSTRENGTHS: [2-3 bullet points]\n\nWEAKNESSES: [2-3 bullet points]\n\nHIRE RECOMMENDATION: [Strong Hire / Pass / Reject]\n\nCONFIDENCE: [High/Medium/Low based on the length of responses]",
        "hasOutputParser": true
      },
      "id": "b5f20497-68a5-4567-9c3a-ec9a1f9cdce3",
